snippet.title: AH Blames JD for her Aquaman 2 On-Set Issues
snippet.description:
In a great article from Poptopic we discuss Amber's delusions that Johnny is causing her depression and stress problems.  When she knows that she caused all of this.  You can check out the article here:
https://poptopic.com.au/lifestyle/celebrities/amber-heard-blames-depp-for-her-fitness-issues-on-aquaman-2-set/
